data.description:
Are you in search of a newer home with no HOA fees and a generous 1/2 acre lot? Look no further! This charming 4-bedroom Florida cottage built by Grahame Homes, nestled in Cross Creek Shores, is move-in ready for its lucky new owner. Constructed in 2020, this delightful split-floorplan home provides ample space for a growing family all on a single level.  Featuring luxurious LVP flooring throughout, attractive countertops in both the kitchen and bathrooms, a spacious dining area, and a generously sized family room, this home boasts a host of fantastic amenities. The master suite is roomy and includes its own en suite and walk in closet, while the children's bedrooms are adorned with tastefully accented walls. Notable updates to this property include the addition of a screened-in back porch and the clearing of the backyard to create more space for outdoor entertainment, whether for kids or adults. There's ample room to consider adding a swimming pool if desired.

Situated conveniently close to the marina and just a short 5-10 minute drive to local elementary, middle, and high schools, this home also offers easy access to the interstate, a mere 10 minutes away. Plus, in just 25 minutes, you can find yourself in the heart of vibrant shopping districts, delightful restaurants, beautiful beaches, and all the treasures the emerald coast has to offer.
